(Aimed at iOS & iOS Simulator, for the rest of the systems I just used the normal build instructions)
Compiled from libogg 1.2.2

Configure line for iOS (in my system):
======================================
PATH=/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/libmikmod/iOS/bin:$PATH CC=/Developer/Platforms/iPhoneOS.platform/Developer/usr/bin/gcc-4.2 CFLAGS="-arch armv6 -isysroot /Developer/Platforms/iPhoneOS.platform/Developer/SDKs/iPhoneOS4.2.sdk/ -I/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/libogg/iOS/include -I/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/libtremor/iOS/include" LDFLAGS="-arch armv6 -isysroot /Developer/Platforms/iPhoneOS.platform/Developer/SDKs/iPhoneOS4.2.sdk/ -L/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/libtremor/iOS/lib" ./configure --prefix=/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/SDL-1.3/iOS/ --with-sdl-prefix=/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/SDL-1.3/iOS/ --disable-shared --enable-static --disable-sdltest --host=arm-apple-darwin10 --enable-music-ogg-tremor --disable-music-native-midi --enable-music-mod

Configure line for iOSSimulator:
================================
PATH=/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/libmikmod/iOSSimulator/bin:$PATH CC=/Developer/Platforms/iPhoneSimulator.platform/Developer/usr/bin/gcc-4.2 CFLAGS="-arch i386 -isysroot /Developer/Platforms/iPhoneSimulator.platform/Developer/SDKs/iPhoneSimulator4.2.sdk -I/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/libogg/iOSSimulator/include/ -I/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/libtremor/iOSSimulator/include" LDFLAGS="-arch i386 -isysroot /Developer/Platforms/iPhoneSimulator.platform/Developer/SDKs/iPhoneSimulator4.2.sdk -L/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/libtremor/iOSSimulator/lib/" ./configure --prefix=/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/SDL-1.3/iOSSimulator/ --with-sdl-prefix=/Users/joseba/cvs/bennugd/monolithic/3rdparty/SDL-1.3/iOSSimulator/ --disable-shared --enable-static --disable-sdltest --host=arm-apple-darwin10 --enable-music-ogg-tremor --disable-music-native-midi --enable-music-mod
